articles.title: Aid delivered to Gaza from newly repaired US-built pier, US official says - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Aid has been delivered into Gaza from a newly repaired American-built pier, after problems that had plagued the effort to bring supplies to Palestinians by sea.
articles.content: Badly needed aid has been delivered into Gaza from a newly repaired American-built pier, a U.S. official said Saturday, following problems that had plagued the effort to bring supplies to Palestinian… [+3755 chars]
